        "item_QhWce7": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Why is the mg count in 82X lower than other brands, yet more effective?",
            "content": "<p><strong>Because in the world of supplements, Bioavailability is King.</strong> Most \"high-dose\" products boast 300,000mg of raw, oversized collagen molecules. However, since the body cannot process that volume, most of it is simply flushed out as waste.</p><p>Our <strong>120,000mg Liposomal formula</strong> is different. By shrinking the collagen into nano-sized bubbles, we ensure <strong>100% utilization</strong> by your cells. You aren't just drinking more collagen; you are actually absorbing more. Remember: <strong>1mg of Liposomal Collagen delivers the power of 10mg of traditional collagen.</strong></p>",
            "open_by_default": true
          }
        },
        "item_U9Dfby": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Will it make me break out like other collagen products?",
            "content": "<p><strong>No—and here is why.</strong> Standard collagen can cause \"internal heat\" and digestive congestion, which often leads to hormonal acne. 82X is the only formula that includes <strong>82 Fermented Plants</strong>. These botanicals act as a natural detoxifier and \"cooling agent,\" ensuring your system stays balanced. You get the glow and the lift without the unwanted breakouts.</p><h3></h3>",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        },
        "item_7bhjeR": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Is it safe for long-term use?",
            "content": "<p>Absolutely. Our formula is designed to work with your body's natural rhythm. By following our <strong>3-Month ON / 1-Month OFF</strong> cycle, you provide your skin with the building blocks it needs while allowing your natural collagen production to stay active and healthy.</p>",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        },
        "item_QDhg4J": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Storage & Use:",
            "content": "<ul><li><strong>Shake well</strong> before every serving to activate the fermented enzymes.</li><li><strong>Keep refrigerated</strong> after opening. This is a bioactive product; cold storage preserves the potency of the live enzymes and ensures every drop is as effective as the first.</li></ul>",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        }
      },
